Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.24,0:02:21.07,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}愛が愛を「重過ぎる」って理解を拒み
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.07,0:02:25.55,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}憎しみに　変わっていく前に…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.55,0:02:27.65,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}何もかもそうだろ?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.65,0:02:32.70,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}バツの悪い事情にはいつも蓋して
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.74,0:02:35.52,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}食わせ物のリアル
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.53,0:02:37.83,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}歪んだジレンマ時代で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.87,0:02:41.79,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}約束したはずの二人さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.80,0:02:46.14,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}気付かず通り過ぎて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:53.57,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}壊しあって　解り合ってたことも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.64,0:02:55.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}置き去りにした
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.48,0:02:58.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}これが成れの果てなの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.97,0:03:03.34,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}認めないで　立ち向かったときも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.10,0:03:09.74,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}落ちて行く時のイメージから逃げ出せずに
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.77,0:03:14.41,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}Ah　何度でも探し出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.45,0:03:21.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}君の目　その手の温もりを
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.21,0:03:24.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}愛はいつも私を傷つけるだけ…って
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.62,0:03:28.27,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}君はつぶやいて　信じる事が
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.29,0:03:31.27,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}怖くて泣いたんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.28,0:03:33.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}弱さを知って強くなれ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.66,0:03:37.23,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}恐れず信じることで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.24,0:03:42.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}本当の愛を知るのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.24,0:02:21.07,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}爱因爱而愈加沉重 却拒绝理解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.07,0:02:25.55,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}在爱变为恨之前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.55,0:02:27.65,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}所有一切皆是如此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.65,0:02:32.70,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}窘迫的永远是这眼前的迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.71,0:02:35.52,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}仿佛被吞噬之物的写实
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.53,0:02:37.83,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}在这被扭曲的进退两难之时代
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.87,0:02:41.79,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}即使海誓山盟的两人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.80,0:02:46.14,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}也渐行着冷漠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:53.57,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}毁灭与理解之物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.64,0:02:55.42,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}早已被遗弃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.48,0:02:58.95,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}这难道是灭亡之尽头？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.97,0:03:03.34,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}否认这一切 挺身面对之时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.10,0:03:09.74,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}即将殒落之时 都不会逃离眼前的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.77,0:03:14.41,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}啊，无论如何也要找寻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.45,0:03:21.09,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}你的双眸 双手的温存
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.21,0:03:24.60,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}说什么「爱总是只给我带来伤害」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.62,0:03:28.27,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}君之低声细语 深信之言
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.29,0:03:31.27,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}是在恐惧中哭泣么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.28,0:03:33.42,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}认识着软弱 渴望着坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.66,0:03:37.23,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}当不再恐惧而满怀信仰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.24,0:03:42.03,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}那将是真实的爱
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----ED
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.68,0:21:52.10,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}純真さが シンプルな力に 変わる 世界に影をつくりだす
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.75,0:22:06.64,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}ガラスケ一スに横たわる 光の存在に触れたくても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.72,0:22:13.74,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}振り上げた手 降ろせなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.11,0:22:22.41,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}落ちるようにしゃがみこんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.54,0:22:30.73,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}Prototype boy 明日の理想だけで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.97,0:22:38.22,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}語り継ぐような 美談にもならないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.43,0:22:45.55,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}この体を失いそうな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.75,0:22:54.72,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}ギリギリの場所が 哀しいくらい似合ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.68,0:21:52.10,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}当纯真变为单纯的力量 世界由此诞生了影子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.75,0:22:06.64,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}穿透过玻璃橱 感触着这光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.72,0:22:13.74,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}举起的手无法放下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.11,0:22:22.41,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}却如同坠落般跌下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.54,0:22:30.73,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}Prototype boy 抛开明天的理想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.97,0:22:38.22,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}即便无法成为传承的美谈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.43,0:22:45.55,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}如同就要失去这副身躯一般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.75,0:22:54.72,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}在极限的边缘 跌入悲伤的深渊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.69,0:00:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,测试体E-57 脑量子波手术完成
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.92,0:00:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入术后观察过程
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.54,0:00:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人吗 有人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.25,0:00:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人能听到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.74,0:00:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑袋里有声音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.59,0:00:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.77,0:00:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.70,0:00:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.11,0:00:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人能听到我的声音吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.14,0:01:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你在和我说话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.58,0:01:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能听到我声音吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.84,0:01:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里 你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.84,0:01:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是就在你面前吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.07,0:01:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.87,0:01:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 能和人说上话真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.76,0:01:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我一直都是孤单一人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.21,0:01:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很感谢你能来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.01,0:01:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.06,0:01:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.49,0:01:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.16,0:01:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.17,0:01:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 我想不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.57,0:01:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.27,0:01:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.72,0:01:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连名字也想不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.53,0:01:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我来给你取个名字好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.46,0:01:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想 你的名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.43,0:01:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就叫阿雷鲁亚好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.00,0:01:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷鲁亚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.71,0:01:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是感谢神的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.83,0:02:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢 感谢什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.34,0:02:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还用说吗 当然是活着这件事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.09,0:02:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毋庸置疑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.36,0:02:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是对我的洗礼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.45,0:03:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.07,0:03:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有5年前阻止了阿扎帝斯坦的内乱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.69,0:04:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对此我表示万分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不进行战斗而阻止了内乱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.42,0:04:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为这种行为是非常可贵的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些事就不提了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.87,0:04:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今后有什么打算
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.33,0:04:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,返回阿扎帝斯坦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.94,0:04:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太胡闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.33,0:04:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保安局会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.72,0:04:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据你的说法 很可能联邦也介入了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.16,0:04:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有加入联邦的阿扎帝斯坦被世界所抛弃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经济崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.85,0:04:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为指导者拉瑟的去世
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.73,0:04:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保守派和改革派陷入战争的泥潭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.98,0:04:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 正因为如此 我才要…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.85,0:04:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 托勒密向阿扎帝斯坦航行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.63,0:04:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.00,0:04:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.80,0:04:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去舰桥了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.38,0:04:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我冒昧的问一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.33,0:04:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是情侣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.26,0:04:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是\N不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.84,0:05:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女的直觉错了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.94,0:05:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪小姐如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.02,0:05:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是没有重新穿上制服的意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.69,0:05:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗 命中率如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.85,0:05:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,78% 78%
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.48,0:05:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不能像哥哥那样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.37,0:05:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.08,0:05:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.48,0:05:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是叫菲露特吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.51,0:05:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经常能感觉到你的视线呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.98,0:05:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.68,0:05:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特喜欢洛克昂 菲露特喜欢洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.84,0:05:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.31,0:05:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.10,0:06:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.13,0:06:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不在乎这些的话 要和我交往嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.62,0:06:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有这个意思的话 之后来我的房间…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.80,0:06:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被甩了 被甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.70,0:06:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.26,0:06:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被比来比去的 谁受得了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能陪我喝一杯么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.76,0:06:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a}阿拉伯海 海上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.57,0:06:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俘虏的Gundam机师被劫走 而且KATARON的人也被救走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是失态啊 大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.33,0:06:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为错误的估计了天行者的战力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.16,0:06:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不听解释 A-LAWS不需要无能的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.58,0:06:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林特少佐 下次的作战由阁下来负责
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.47,0:07:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.75,0:07:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我来教教您A-LAWS的战斗方法吧 大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.29,0:07:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请一定让我学习一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.16,0:07:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.01,0:07:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅长扫荡战的阿尔巴·林特少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.31,0:07:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然把那个臭名昭著的男人招来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.49,0:07:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据保安局的证言 Gundam好像把关押中的阿扎帝斯坦皇女带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.73,0:07:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下怎么看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.56,0:07:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说Gundam机师里有中东出身的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.36,0:07:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算为了年轻的公主殿下去当白马王子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.67,0:07:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我推测现在天行者正在为私情而行动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.85,0:07:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮助作为机师的伙伴就是最好的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.63,0:07:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.57,0:07:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这附近张网以待应该是最好的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.22,0:07:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 允许你使用Trilobite
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢 还有件事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.44,0:08:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本次作战希望也能让他参加
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.05,0:08:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr.武士道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.44,0:08:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅不到5分钟的闪电战
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.46,0:08:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰船沉入海中 激发海啸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.33,0:08:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受此影响 部队陷入混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.66,0:08:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周围湿度上升 导致粒子武器的效力减半
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.13,0:08:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有四架Gundam的合作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.65,0:08:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大胆与细致共存的战术
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.26,0:08:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里看到过…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.71,0:08:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Trilobite准备出发 Trilobite准备出发
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.51,0:08:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Trilobite？ 资料中的新型机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.37,0:08:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然开发了搭载GN DRIVE的MA
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.50,0:08:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说是有位女性捐赠了巨额的资金
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.02,0:09:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好事者真多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对第四小队下达了降落地面的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.74,0:09:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈勒维准尉 请立刻到舰桥来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.04,0:09:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.67,0:09:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS队准备出发
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.71,0:09:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到了G1传来的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.86,0:09:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子 果然是朝阿扎帝斯坦而去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.61,0:09:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要这么做吗 克劳斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.74,0:09:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我们的目的而言 天行者是不可缺少的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 帮助他们的话也可以保护玛丽娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.27,0:09:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.56,0:09:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要帮助她 你重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.44,0:09:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.62,0:09:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说要离开王宫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.38,0:09:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下 就现在联邦政府的政策而言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.05,0:09:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这个国家加入联邦 也没有未来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.60,0:10:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我要用我自己的方法来创造这个国家的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.30,0:10:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿扎帝斯坦不能采用的你的方法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.89,0:10:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅是让这个国家站起来是没有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.33,0:10:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳斯 让我也和部队一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.56,0:10:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.19,0:10:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会拖后腿的 拜托了 克劳斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.02,0:10:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该有我能做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.56,0:10:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.94,0:10:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 要不要和我一起来 到阿扎帝斯坦来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.08,0:10:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想建立一个没有纷争 大家都能正常生活的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.14,0:10:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.33,0:10:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所能做的只有战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.61,0:10:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说这么悲伤的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:11:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 战争不会孕育任何东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.42,0:11:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.14,0:11:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在进入天行者之前 我也是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 确实有自破坏之中诞生的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.50,0:11:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了未来 世界的扭曲就由Gundam来纠正
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.42,0:11:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我和Gundam一起战斗的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.60,0:11:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深度 固定在3200
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.94,0:11:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…没关系么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.07,0:11:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看到这种机密
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.61,0:11:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人手不足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.56,0:11:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是有宇宙技师的二级执照么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.25,0:11:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说了 不劳动就没饭吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.70,0:11:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.30,0:11:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我伊恩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊恩·维斯迪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.72,0:12:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊恩先生 你为何会来到此处呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.37,0:12:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对战争深恶痛绝 希望能根绝之
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.93,0:12:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里每个人都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.10,0:12:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有被送到最前线战斗之人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.98,0:12:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被军队进行了肉体改造之人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.49,0:12:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被恐怖袭击夺去亲属之人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.02,0:12:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被游击队培养成长之人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.83,0:12:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在战争中失去了最重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.10,0:12:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界就是这么现实的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.15,0:12:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我们就是罪犯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.40,0:12:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总会遭到报应的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.79,0:12:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在战争被根绝之后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.76,0:12:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索玛·皮瑞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.36,0:12:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得 是人革联的超兵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.17,0:12:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么之前没发觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.00,0:12:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能介入我的脑量子波的 只有玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.22,0:12:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被国联军抓到的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.44,0:13:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉是到了偿还罪孽的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.61,0:13:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至觉得就那样腐朽风化掉也好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.91,0:13:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 现在不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.54,0:13:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想把玛丽找回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方是敌人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.20,0:13:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.61,0:13:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你 已经把超人机关的设施给…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.94,0:13:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.60,0:13:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把自己的同胞们杀掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.61,0:13:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽如果知道这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.23,0:13:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会恨我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.40,0:13:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做的 就是这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.10,0:13:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 就算是会被憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.74,0:13:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人羡慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.05,0:13:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.49,0:13:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经 找到战斗的理由了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.68,0:13:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的战斗之中 有那样的理由么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.84,0:13:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是赞同了伊奥利亚的计划才参加进来的么?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.86,0:13:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.63,0:13:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时想着要消除战争
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.73,0:13:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 除了那一点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时的我还想要把自己不祥的过去抹杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.12,0:14:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不祥的过去…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.26,0:14:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是抱着这样的想法战斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.54,0:14:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.77,0:14:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为了坚持自我 让很多的生命就那么牺牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.79,0:14:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.99,0:14:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我抹杀不掉过去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.69,0:14:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对现在的我来说 已经没有战斗的理由了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.33,0:14:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在这里的理由也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.24,0:14:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有留在这里的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.39,0:14:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这么觉得的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.48,0:14:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种安慰…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.26,0:14:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 为什么你会救了我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.82,0:14:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗的理由 一定能找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.59,0:14:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是你的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.11,0:14:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arios Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios的后继机体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.05,0:14:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用这架机体 就用Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.66,0:14:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会把玛丽找回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.94,0:14:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算哈雷鲁亚已经不在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.62,0:14:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑量子波不能再用也好…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.63,0:14:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗的理由么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.03,0:14:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去的我会否定这个概念吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.88,0:15:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂  克丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.07,0:15:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里希特 莫雷诺先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.33,0:15:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还能够再来一次么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.28,0:15:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站在整个世界的对面…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.04,0:15:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 守护自己重要的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.32,0:15:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米里奥…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.75,0:15:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密号 马上要穿过霍尔木兹海峡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.04,0:15:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…这周围太安静了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.04,0:15:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱼群的样子也有点… 在这个深度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.01,0:15:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.60,0:15:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,E声纳出现反应
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.84,0:15:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6个敌目标正高速接近中的说!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是鱼雷!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.74,0:15:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.67,0:15:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN力场 最大展开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.07,0:15:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.60,0:15:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌袭!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.06,0:15:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在鱼雷里有重化合物…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.18,0:15:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声纳被无效化了的说!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.04,0:15:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有能在这个深度活动的敌人?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.43,0:15:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型机!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.00,0:16:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在计划地点拖住敌舰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.58,0:16:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要入虎穴夺子了!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.17,0:16:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去舰艇中央部分!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.95,0:16:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.21,0:16:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第2波 要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.49,0:16:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大型鱼雷两发!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.51,0:16:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN力场 被突破了的说!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.42,0:16:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新武器么!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.45,0:16:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下部荚舱进水!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.60,0:16:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算要Gundam出击 这种深度下也…!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让托勒密号浮上了!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到Gundam能承受的深度!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.89,0:16:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从海上来的爆雷…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.93,0:16:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可能在使用的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.83,0:16:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化学爆弹!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.45,0:16:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2分钟的爆破之后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用Trilobite进行接近战
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.84,0:16:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法拜见敌舰被压碎的情景倒是有点可惜…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.71,0:16:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林特少佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.15,0:17:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索敌到前期行动为止都很出色
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.24,0:17:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 对方的指挥官会出什么招呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.95,0:17:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船体被覆盖上树脂 炮门无法打开!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.99,0:17:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舵也不行了!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.20,0:17:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 敌人在哪!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.03,0:17:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,E声纳 不能使用的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.20,0:17:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没什么对策么!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.36,0:17:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.31,0:17:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对策是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.46,0:17:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪小姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.68,0:17:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上爆雷就会停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.00,0:17:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着 海里的敌人正在向这里接近
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.92,0:17:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备直接攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.59,0:17:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人 突击舰体左舷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.18,0:17:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,损 损害很大!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.41,0:17:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去 被压坏的危险也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.87,0:17:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真够幸运的 我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.43,0:17:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到的敌人就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密号已经到了Gundam可以出击的深度
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:18:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且敌人连下部荚舱的注水时间都替我们省了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.74,0:18:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比MS的推力的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.59,0:18:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这部Trilobite才不会…!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.21,0:18:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边还有王牌 TRANS-AM!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.31,0:18:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟 竟然会!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.54,0:18:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算在水中 有这么接近的话…!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.54,0:18:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉开距离 用鱼雷!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.00,0:18:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.77,0:18:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OO 将目标…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.06,0:18:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不和我一起来么?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.09,0:18:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去阿扎帝斯坦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.69,0:18:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…将目标
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.12,0:18:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱逐!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.22,0:19:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不可能!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.56,0:19:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Trilobite竟然!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.70,0:19:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 要冲出海面了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.86,0:19:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.05,0:19:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.52,0:19:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.75,0:19:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是… 是Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.76,0:19:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说 Trilobite已经…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.61,0:19:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让本舰后退
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.07,0:19:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让MS队出击!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.22,0:19:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经太晚了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架Ahead是!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.26,0:19:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr.武士道!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.13,0:19:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS的新型机!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.19,0:19:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种动作!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.36,0:19:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…麻烦的家伙么!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.68,0:19:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那份剑术…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.56,0:20:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会错 就是那个时候的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.93,0:20:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何等侥幸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.65,0:20:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍辱苟活下来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.60,0:20:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也终于有价值了!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.19,0:20:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架机体 测试体E-57!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.79,0:20:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是机体的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.78,0:20:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的能力…!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.60,0:20:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.74,0:20:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坠落吧 Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.48,0:20:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.77,0:20:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是 KATARON?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.07,0:20:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.66,0:20:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反政府组织么!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.64,0:20:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别挡我的道!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.25,0:20:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退 重整阵势
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.78,0:20:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.80,0:20:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉… 拒绝和我交手么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.69,0:21:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的领教到了不少哦 少佐阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.96,0:21:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反政府组织KATARON
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.64,0:21:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有如此的战力…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.08,0:21:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会是谁呢? 想要见我的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.85,0:21:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了呢 玛丽娜·伊斯玛依露
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.61,0:21:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 诗琳…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.01,0:21:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诗琳·帕索提娅…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.00,0:21:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.44,0:21:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在是KATARON的成员
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.05,0:21:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个对地球联邦的行径高喊反调的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.00,0:23:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于下定决心了么 比利
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.15,0:23:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来还望多多照顾 叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.60,0:23:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里要称呼我司令
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.07,0:23:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任命你 继承已故的列夫曼教授的事业
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.14,0:23:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担任新型MS的开发主任
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.95,0:23:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,领命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.09,0:23:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.23,0:23:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.32,0:23:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小不合适 好紧…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.94,0:23:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 马上去再准备一件
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.85,0:23:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我说这样才好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.84,0:23:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是性骚扰的说 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.02,0:23:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪·李·诺莉艾卡…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.27,0:23:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久篠…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.33,0:23:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从很久以前开始 就一直在利用我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.83,0:23:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后又践踏了…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.10,0:23:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的那份心意
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.38,0:24:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被A-LAWS近乎毫无慈悲的攻击左右的机师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.53,0:24:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后刹那在红莲之炎中 将品味如戏的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.12,0:24:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 故国炎上
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.57,0:24:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份再会 如同一剂猛药么


